# Tacet — local secrets template.
#
# Copy this file to `.dev.vars` (which is git-ignored) to run locally with real
# secrets, or skip it entirely: `npm run dev` works with safe local fallbacks and
# needs NONE of these. These matter only when you deploy to your own Cloudflare
# account. Never commit real values.

# Signs the session cookie. Generate a strong random value for any real deployment:
#   openssl rand -hex 32
# Local dev uses a built-in throwaway fallback if this is unset.
SESSION_SECRET="replace-with-a-long-random-string"

# Cloudflare Turnstile (bot protection on registration). Optional — the challenge
# is only enforced when both are set. Get them from the Cloudflare dashboard.
TURNSTILE_SECRET=""
TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY=""
